query.sfwSql: DELETE FROM SGT_5500_REPORT WHERE COMPUTATION_YEAR = @COMPUTATION_YEAR DELETE FROM SGT_SSA_5500_REPORT_DETAILS WHERE PLAN_YEAR = @COMPUTATION_YEAR

-- CODE 'A' SELECT DISTINCT 'A' AS MPI_5500_STATUS_CODE, SP.SSN, SP.FIRST_NAME, SUBSTRING(SP.MIDDLE_NAME,1,1) AS MIDDLE_NAME, SP.LAST_NAME, 'C' AS TYPE_OF_ANNUITY, 'E' AS PAYMENT_FREQUENCY, ISNULL(ACCRUED_BENEFIT_TILL_LAST_COMP_YEAR,0) AS DB_PAYMENT, 0 AS UNITS_SHARES, 0 AS TOTAL_VALUE_ACCOUNT, YEAR(GETDATE()) - 1 AS PLAN_YEAR_SEPERATED, 'Y' AS VESTED, 'PENSION' AS PLAN_IDENTIFIER FROM SGT_DATA_EXTRACTION_BATCH_INFO DATA INNER JOIN SGT_PERSON SP ON DATA.PERSON_SSN = SP.SSN INNER JOIN SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT SPA ON SPA.PERSON_ID = SP.PERSON_ID AND spa.PLAN_ID = 2 INNER JOIN SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT_ELIGIBILITY E ON E.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID = SPA.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID left outer join SGT_SSA_5500_REPORT_DETAILS d on SP.ssn = d.ssn and d.plan_identifier = 'PENSION' WHERE DATA.BENEFICIARY_FLAG = 'M' AND DATA.BENEFICIARY_ID IS NULL and d.ssn is null AND ISNULL(DATA.Last_QF_YR_BEFORE_BIS,0) = YEAR(GETDATE()) - 1 AND VESTED_DATE IS NOT NULL AND YEAR_END_DATA_EXTRACTION_HEADER_ID =(select year_end_data_extraction_header_id from SGT_YEAR_END_DATA_EXTRACTION_HEADER a where a.[YEAR] = YEAR(GETDATE()) - 1) and DATA.PLAN_ID = 2 and sp.DATE_OF_DEATH is null AND STATUS_CODE_VALUE ='C' AND ISNULL(ACCRUED_BENEFIT_TILL_LAST_COMP_YEAR,0) > 0
UNION -- CODE 'B' SELECT DISTINCT 'B' AS MPI_5500_STATUS_CODE, SP.SSN, SP.FIRST_NAME, SUBSTRING(SP.MIDDLE_NAME,1,1) AS MIDDLE_NAME, SP.LAST_NAME, 'C' AS TYPE_OF_ANNUITY, 'E' AS PAYMENT_FREQUENCY, ISNULL(DATA.ACCRUED_BENEFIT_TILL_LAST_COMP_YEAR,0) AS DB_PAYMENT, 0 AS UNITS_SHARES, 0 AS TOTAL_VALUE_ACCOUNT, YEAR(GETDATE()) - 1 AS PLAN_YEAR_SEPERATED, 'Y' AS VESTED, 'PENSION' AS PLAN_IDENTIFIER FROM SGT_DATA_EXTRACTION_BATCH_INFO DATA INNER JOIN SGT_PERSON SP ON DATA.PERSON_SSN = SP.SSN INNER JOIN SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT SPA ON SPA.PERSON_ID = SP.PERSON_ID AND spa.PLAN_ID = 2 INNER JOIN SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT_ELIGIBILITY E ON E.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID = SPA.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID INNER JOIN SGT_SSA_5500_REPORT_DETAILS d on SP.ssn = d.ssn and d.plan_identifier = 'PENSION' AND D.CODE <> 'D' INNER JOIN SGT_DATA_EXTRACTION_BATCH_INFO PRIOR_DATA ON DATA.PERSON_SSN = PRIOR_DATA.PERSON_SSN AND DATA.PLAN_ID = PRIOR_DATA.PLAN_ID AND PRIOR_DATA.YEAR_END_DATA_EXTRACTION_HEADER_ID = (select year_end_data_extraction_header_id from SGT_YEAR_END_DATA_EXTRACTION_HEADER a where a.[YEAR] = YEAR(GETDATE()) - 2) AND DATA.ACCRUED_BENEFIT_TILL_LAST_COMP_YEAR <> PRIOR_DATA.ACCRUED_BENEFIT_TILL_LAST_COMP_YEAR LEFT OUTER JOIN SGT_PAYMENT_HISTORY_HEADER PHH ON SP.PERSON_ID = PHH.PERSON_ID AND PHH.PLAN_ID = 2 LEFT OUTER JOIN SGT_PAYMENT_HISTORY_DISTRIBUTION PHD ON PHH.PAYMENT_HISTORY_HEADER_ID = PHD.PAYMENT_HISTORY_HEADER_ID AND PHD.DISTRIBUTION_STATUS_VALUE = 'CLRD' LEFT OUTER JOIN SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT_PAYMENT_ITEM_TYPE PAPIT ON PHH.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID = PAPIT.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID AND PAPIT.PAYMENT_ITEM_TYPE_ID IN(1,2) INNER JOIN ( select distinct SP.SSN from [PILLARS].[DBO].[MPI_WorkHistory] wh --inner join eadb..hours h on r.reportid = h.reportid and r.pensionyear in(YEAR(GETDATE()) - 2,YEAR(GETDATE()) - 1) and r.HoursStatus = 0 Inner join SGT_PERSON SP ON wh.MPIPersonId = SP.MPI_PERSON_ID AND WH.ComputationYear in(YEAR(GETDATE()) - 2,YEAR(GETDATE()) - 1) and wh.HoursStatus = 0 group by SP.SSN having sum(case when wh.ComputationYear = YEAR(GETDATE()) - 2 then wh.HoursWorked else 0 end) < 200 and sum(case when wh.ComputationYear = YEAR(GETDATE()) - 1 then wh.HoursWorked else 0 end) < 200 ) EA_HOURS ON SP.SSN = EA_HOURS.SSN WHERE DATA.BENEFICIARY_FLAG = 'M' AND DATA.BENEFICIARY_ID IS NULL and d.SSN IS NOT NULL AND PAPIT.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID IS NULL AND ISNULL(DATA.Last_QF_YR_BEFORE_BIS,0) = YEAR(GETDATE()) - 1 AND VESTED_DATE IS NOT NULL AND DATA.YEAR_END_DATA_EXTRACTION_HEADER_ID =(select year_end_data_extraction_header_id from SGT_YEAR_END_DATA_EXTRACTION_HEADER a where a.[YEAR] = YEAR(GETDATE()) - 1) and DATA.PLAN_ID = 2 and sp.DATE_OF_DEATH is null AND DATA.STATUS_CODE_VALUE ='C'
UNION -- CODE 'D' SELECT DISTINCT 'D' AS MPI_5500_STATUS_CODE, SP.SSN, SP.FIRST_NAME, SUBSTRING(SP.MIDDLE_NAME,1,1) AS MIDDLE_NAME, SP.LAST_NAME, 'C' AS TYPE_OF_ANNUITY, 'E' AS PAYMENT_FREQUENCY, 0 AS DB_PAYMENT, 0 AS UNITS_SHARES, 0 AS TOTAL_VALUE_ACCOUNT, YEAR(GETDATE()) - 1 AS PLAN_YEAR_SEPERATED, 'Y' AS VESTED, 'PENSION' AS PLAN_IDENTIFIER FROM SGT_SSA_5500_REPORT_DETAILS SSA INNER JOIN SGT_PERSON SP ON SSA.SSN = SP.SSN INNER JOIN ( SELECT PHH.PERSON_ID, MIN(PHH.PAYMENT_DATE) AS PAYMENT_DATE FROM SGT_SSA_5500_REPORT_DETAILS SSA INNER JOIN SGT_PERSON SP ON SSA.SSN = SP.SSN INNER JOIN SGT_PAYMENT_HISTORY_HEADER PHH ON SP.PERSON_ID = PHH.PERSON_ID INNER JOIN SGT_PAYMENT_HISTORY_DISTRIBUTION PHD ON PHH.PAYMENT_HISTORY_HEADER_ID = PHD.PAYMENT_HISTORY_HEADER_ID AND PHD.DISTRIBUTION_STATUS_VALUE IN('CLRD','RSUD') INNER JOIN SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT_PAYMENT_ITEM_TYPE PAPIT ON PHH.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID = PAPIT.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID AND PAPIT.PAYMENT_ITEM_TYPE_ID IN(1,2) WHERE PLAN_ID = 2 GROUP BY PHH.PERSON_ID ) AS PAY ON SP.PERSON_ID = PAY.PERSON_ID AND YEAR(PAY.PAYMENT_DATE) < YEAR(GETDATE()) WHERE SSA.PLAN_IDENTIFIER = 'PENSION' AND SSA.SSN NOT IN (SELECT SSN FROM SGT_SSA_5500_REPORT_DETAILS WHERE CODE = 'D' and PLAN_YEAR < YEAR(GETDATE())) order by SP.SSN

-- CODE 'A' SELECT DISTINCT 'A' AS IAP_5500_STATUS_CODE, SP.SSN, SP.FIRST_NAME, SUBSTRING(SP.MIDDLE_NAME,1,1) AS MIDDLE_NAME, SP.LAST_NAME, 'A' AS TYPE_OF_ANNUITY, 'A' AS PAYMENT_FREQUENCY, 0 AS DB_PAYMENT, 0 AS UNITS_SHARES, ISNULL(A.ENDING_BALANCE,0) AS TOTAL_VALUE_ACCOUNT, YEAR(GETDATE()) - 1 AS PLAN_YEAR_SEPERATED, 'Y' AS VESTED, 'IAP' AS PLAN_IDENTIFIER from ( select person_Account_id, sum(isnull(ending_balance,0)) as ending_balance from sgt_iap_allocation_detail where computation_year = YEAR(GETDATE()) - 1 --and iap_allocation_category_value = 'VBIS' AND ENDING_BALANCE > 100 group by person_account_id )a inner join sgt_person_account SPA on a.person_account_id = SPA.person_account_id inner join sgt_person SP on SPA.person_id = SP.person_id inner join ( select person_ssn from SGT_DATA_EXTRACTION_BATCH_INFO where ISNULL(Last_QF_YR_BEFORE_BIS,0) = YEAR(GETDATE()) - 1 and beneficiary_flag = 'M' except select person_ssn from SGT_DATA_EXTRACTION_BATCH_INFO where ISNULL(Last_QF_YR_BEFORE_BIS,0) > 0 and ISNULL(Last_QF_YR_BEFORE_BIS,0) < YEAR(GETDATE()) - 1 and beneficiary_flag = 'M' )d on SP.ssn = d.person_ssn LEFT OUTER JOIN SGT_SSA_5500_REPORT_DETAILS SSA ON SP.SSN = SSA.SSN AND SSA.PLAN_IDENTIFIER = 'IAP' LEFT OUTER JOIN SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT_ELIGIBILITY E ON SPA.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID = E.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID WHERE A.ENDING_BALANCE > 100 AND E.VESTED_DATE IS NOT NULL AND SSA.SSN IS NULL
UNION -- CODE 'B' SELECT DISTINCT 'B' AS IAP_5500_STATUS_CODE, SP.SSN, SP.FIRST_NAME, SUBSTRING(SP.MIDDLE_NAME,1,1) AS MIDDLE_NAME, SP.LAST_NAME, 'A' AS TYPE_OF_ANNUITY, 'A' AS PAYMENT_FREQUENCY, 0 AS DB_PAYMENT, 0 AS UNITS_SHARES, ISNULL(A.ENDING_BALANCE,0) AS TOTAL_VALUE_ACCOUNT, YEAR(GETDATE()) - 1 AS PLAN_YEAR_SEPERATED, 'Y' AS VESTED, 'IAP' AS PLAN_IDENTIFIER FROM ( SELECT PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID,SUM(ISNULL(ENDING_BALANCE,0)) ENDING_BALANCE FROM SGT_IAP_ALLOCATION_DETAIL ID WHERE ID.IAP_ALLOCATION_CATEGORY_VALUE IN ( 'VBIS' ) AND COMPUTATION_YEAR = YEAR(GETDATE()) - 1 GROUP BY ID.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID )A INNER JOIN SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT SPA ON A.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID =SPA.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID INNER JOIN SGT_PERSON SP ON SP.PERSON_ID = SPA.PERSON_ID INNER JOIN SGT_IAP_ALLOCATION_DETAIL I ON I.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID = SPA.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID AND I.COMPUTATION_YEAR= YEAR(GETDATE()) - 2 AND I.ENDING_BALANCE <> A.ENDING_BALANCE INNER JOIN SGT_SSA_5500_REPORT_DETAILS SSA ON SSA.SSN = SP.SSN AND SSA.PLAN_IDENTIFIER = 'IAP' LEFT OUTER JOIN SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT_ELIGIBILITY E ON SPA.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID = E.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID LEFT OUTER JOIN SGT_PAYMENT_HISTORY_HEADER PHH ON SP.PERSON_ID = PHH.PERSON_ID AND PHH.PLAN_ID = 1 LEFT OUTER JOIN SGT_PAYMENT_HISTORY_DISTRIBUTION PHD ON PHH.PAYMENT_HISTORY_HEADER_ID = PHD.PAYMENT_HISTORY_HEADER_ID AND PHD.DISTRIBUTION_STATUS_VALUE = 'CLRD' LEFT OUTER JOIN SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT_PAYMENT_ITEM_TYPE PAPIT ON PHH.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID = PAPIT.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID AND PAPIT.PAYMENT_ITEM_TYPE_ID = 21 --INNER JOIN --( --select h.SSN --from eadb..report r --inner join eadb..hours h on r.reportid = h.reportid and r.pensionyear in(YEAR(GETDATE()) - 2,YEAR(GETDATE()) - 1) and r.Status = 0 --group by h.SSN having sum(case when r.PensionYear = YEAR(GETDATE()) - 2 then h.HoursWorked else 0 end) < 200 and sum(case when r.PensionYear = YEAR(GETDATE()) - 1 then h.HoursWorked else 0 end) < 200 --) EA_HOURS ON SP.SSN = EA_HOURS.SSN --WHERE A.ENDING_BALANCE > 100 AND E.VESTED_DATE IS NOT NULL AND PAPIT.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID IS NULL
INNER JOIN ( select distinct SP.SSN from [PILLARS].[DBO].[MPI_WorkHistory] wh --inner join eadb..hours h on r.reportid = h.reportid and r.pensionyear in(YEAR(GETDATE()) - 2,YEAR(GETDATE()) - 1) and r.HoursStatus = 0 Inner join SGT_PERSON SP ON wh.MPIPersonId = SP.MPI_PERSON_ID AND WH.ComputationYear in(YEAR(GETDATE()) - 2,YEAR(GETDATE()) - 1) and wh.HoursStatus = 0 group by SP.SSN having sum(case when wh.ComputationYear = YEAR(GETDATE()) - 2 then wh.HoursWorked else 0 end) < 200 and sum(case when wh.ComputationYear = YEAR(GETDATE()) - 1 then wh.HoursWorked else 0 end) < 200 ) EA_HOURS ON SP.SSN = EA_HOURS.SSN WHERE A.ENDING_BALANCE > 100 AND E.VESTED_DATE IS NOT NULL AND PAPIT.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID IS NULL UNION -- CODE 'D' SELECT DISTINCT 'D' AS IAP_5500_STATUS_CODE, SP.SSN, SP.FIRST_NAME, SUBSTRING(SP.MIDDLE_NAME,1,1) AS MIDDLE_NAME, SP.LAST_NAME, 'A' AS TYPE_OF_ANNUITY, 'A' AS PAYMENT_FREQUENCY, 0 AS DB_PAYMENT, 0 AS UNITS_SHARES, 0 AS TOTAL_VALUE_ACCOUNT, YEAR(GETDATE()) - 1 AS PLAN_YEAR_SEPERATED, 'Y' AS VESTED, 'IAP' AS PLAN_IDENTIFIER FROM SGT_SSA_5500_REPORT_DETAILS SSA INNER JOIN SGT_PERSON SP ON SSA.SSN = SP.SSN INNER JOIN SGT_PAYMENT_HISTORY_HEADER PHH ON PHH.PERSON_ID = SP.PERSON_ID AND PLAN_ID = 1 and year(PHH.PAYMENT_DATE) = YEAR(GETDATE()) - 1 INNER JOIN SGT_PAYMENT_HISTORY_DISTRIBUTION PHD ON PHH.PAYMENT_HISTORY_HEADER_ID = PHD.PAYMENT_HISTORY_HEADER_ID AND PHD.DISTRIBUTION_STATUS_VALUE = 'CLRD' WHERE SSA.PLAN_IDENTIFIER = 'IAP'
SELECT TOP(1) COMPUTATION_YEAR FROM dbo.SGT_IAP_ALLOCATION_DETAIL ORDER BY COMPUTATION_YEAR DESC
